{"type":null,"faqId":45334,"title":"荣耀盒子M321的 DLNA 功能如何使用？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">方式一：</span><span>通过荣耀盒子M321，将手机上的本地视频推送到电视上播放。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 1  </span><span>将手机和盒子连接至同一个家庭网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 2  </span><span>在手机上下载 DLNA 客户端软件。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 3  </span><span>在手机上启动 DLNA 客户端，共享或推送手机上的视频到电视上播放。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">方式二：</span><span>共享 Window7 电脑上的流媒体文件，在电视上播放。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 1  </span><span>将 Window7 电脑和荣耀盒子M321连接至同一个家庭网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 2  </span><span>在电脑上打开 Windows Media Player，选择“</span><span class=\"s1\">媒体流</span><span>”依次选择“</span><span class=\"s1\">打开媒体流</span><span>”、“</span><span class=\"s1\">允许远程控制我的播放器</span><span>”、“</span><span class=\"s1\">自动允许设备播放我的媒体</span><span>”，根据界面指引完成共享操作。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 3  </span><span>进入盒子“</span><span class=\"s1\">媒体中心</span><span>”，找到电脑共享的流媒体文件，点击即可播放。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>若按照上诉操作无法正常使用，请向电脑的生产商咨询如何使用。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":245,"faqType":"多屏互动","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"855","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Screen-Sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442556874000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M321,MediaQ M321-20","visitedTimes":61,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"DLNA,使用,荣耀盒子","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}